snippet.title: Best VGM 2108 - The Elder Scrolls IV : Oblivion - Watchman's Ease
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 68 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mkTkAkcj6mQ
Best VGM 1745 - http://youtu.be/QTwpZhWtQus

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / Xbox 360 / PS3
The Elder Scroll IV: Oblivion (2006)
Watchman's Ease
Jeremy Soule
